{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":8,"day":14}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"一盆热水","authors":["雷厉"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条毛巾雪白洁净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盆热水升腾白烟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花白头发掖进帽里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她端水来到重伤员床前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解开衬衣轻轻地擦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶着身子慢慢地翻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动作有如鹅毛轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根根神经紧相连！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强的战士铁打的汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受伤时不见泪珠转；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手术台上不哼一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么此刻眼角亮闪闪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪滚滚涌出眶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话语出口唇发颤："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“院长呵，您热水擦在咱身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的深情哟暖心坎……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院长舒眉笑微微——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我呀，也在擦脑里的旧观念。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，脸盆里，映出一颗丹心似红火炭！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}